==Igduden==

Deg Ugafa n Tefriqt, imezdaγen ines'liyen neγ imezdaγen-imenza d [[Imaziγen]], d nitni ay d amur ameqran deg yimezdaγen n [[Tamazγa|Tmazγa]], xas ma yella at'as deg-sen ass-a i la ttmeslayen [[taεrabt]] ukk d/neγ d Tafransist. Imaziγen egan-ed tilas i wakal d ameqran, yewwet-ed seg wemda n [[Siwa]], deg Utaram (West) n [[Mas'er]] aramma d Targa Zewwaγen (tazeggart) d [[Muritanya]], af (γef) yiri n ugaraw Atlasi neγ adrar n watlas.

Akal n Yimaziγen, seg wakken meqqer aramma ay yewwed' γer wul (tlemmast) n Tefriqt. D [[Imuhaγ]] neγ Imucaγ ay d agdud n Yimaziγen ay lin (yesεan) akal meqqren akk gar igduden imaziγen wiyyad', xas akken ur ttuggtan ara. Akal-nsen d [[Aneεruf]] (Idurar n Tasili, n Ayer di [[Niger]], atg.).

